    <data key="d0">Vertex Pharmaceuticals Molecule Search Platform</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nflGdpwbf54</data>
    <data key="d2">Serverless, on-demand molecular search architecture utilizing ECS, Fargate Spot, and Amazon MQ to run up to 500 parallel worker tasks.</data>
    <data key="d3">compute_intensive, interactive</data>
    <data key="d4">True</data>
